Package: randomifyR
Title: Produces random samples of data
Version: 0.3.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Learn", "R", , "dev@arp.numbat.space", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Facilitates efficient and unbiased random sampling of data from 
    diverse datasets. Leveraging advanced random sampling algorithms, this 
    package enables users to extract representative subsets of data for 
    analysis, modeling, and validation purposes.
